message:
Please note..not being able to conceive doesn’t mean you cannot conceive. In today's time, conception is possible in 90 per cent of complicated issues as well.

Can you first tell me for how long have you and your partner been trying to conceive without any protection?
Less than 6 months
More than 6 months but less than a year
other_symptoms: Trying for more than 6 months but less than a year

message: More than 1 year

Alright..

Do you think that your erections during the sexual activity are not as good or long as you want them to be?

message:
Not to worry at all, most of the time, that’s treatable..

additional_information: Erectile Dysfunction (ED) happens when a penis owner has ongoing problems getting and keeping an erection. Without treatment, ED can make sex difficult. The problem is commonly reported by 1 in 5 men and may increase with age.
general_advice: Exercices like Kegel and yoga can be very helpful to cure ED.|Relationship therapy, healthy lifestyle, healthy food habits and relationship therapy ( if required) are best advised for ED patients.

additional_information: Ejaculation issues can be of four types, Premature ejaculation, delayed ejaculation, retrograde ejaculation or no ejaculation. All can cause delay/problem in conception. It is mostly treatable with the right medical advise.
general_advice: Some self-help techniques for dealing with premature ejaculation|Exercising regularly|Consuming food rich in zinc and magnesium, as they may help increase the time to climax.| Using thick condoms to reduce sensation |Masturbating 1- 2 hours before sex

general_advice: A healthy relationship helps one face any challenges together.|Also healthy relationship will bring in more intimacy and is thus always good to increase chances of fertility.
